txt.en: 'Stay away! The Bloodletter wants the cages returned to Udûn to bring more slaves!'
'Burudagath the Bloodletter has the blood of the true-Men, not like these weak slaves!'
'They fell easily, and now so will you!'
'The Bloodletter doesn't need to know the slaves revolted on the way! We'll bring you to Faltor-shík instead!'
'You'll make a fine sacrifice... and I'll eat what's left of you when the Master's finished!'
